source.query:
SELECT * FROM (
WITH CURR_CLN_DATE AS (
SELECT TRIM(CONCAT_WS('~',REGEXP_REPLACE(WS_EXT_PH_PART_NUM, ' +', ''),WS_EXT_PH_PLAN_NUM,WS_EXT_PH_CLIENT_ID),'~') SOURCE_KEY,SUBSTR(WS_EXT_PH_PART_NUM,1,9) WS_EXT_PH_PART_NUM,
WS_EXT_PH_NAME,WS_EXT_PH_BRTH_DATE,WS_EXT_PH_ADDR_L1,WS_EXT_PH_ADDR_L2,WS_EXT_PH_ADDR_L3,WS_EXT_PH_CITY,WS_EXT_PH_STATE,WS_EXT_PH_ZIP,WS_EXT_PH_OMNI_VERSION,
MD5(IFF(SUBSTR(WS_EXT_PH_PART_NUM,1,9) IS NULL,'0',SUBSTR(WS_EXT_PH_PART_NUM,1,9))||IFF(WS_EXT_PH_NAME IS NULL,'1',WS_EXT_PH_NAME)||IFF(WS_EXT_PH_BRTH_DATE IS NULL,'2',WS_EXT_PH_BRTH_DATE)||
    IFF(WS_EXT_PH_ADDR_L1 IS NULL,'3',WS_EXT_PH_ADDR_L1)||IFF(WS_EXT_PH_ADDR_L2 IS NULL,'4',WS_EXT_PH_ADDR_L2)||IFF(WS_EXT_PH_ADDR_L3 IS NULL,'5',WS_EXT_PH_ADDR_L3)||IFF(WS_EXT_PH_CITY IS NULL,'6',WS_EXT_PH_CITY)||
    IFF(WS_EXT_PH_STATE IS NULL,'7',WS_EXT_PH_STATE)||IFF(WS_EXT_PH_ZIP IS NULL,'8',WS_EXT_PH_ZIP)) CHECK_SUM
FROM MYVOYAGE_CLEANSED.RS_OMNI_VIPS_DAILY_PART_HEADER_CLN)
SELECT 
CASE WHEN A.SOURCE_KEY IS NULL THEN B.SOURCE_KEY ELSE A.SOURCE_KEY END SOURCE_KEY,
CASE WHEN A.WS_EXT_PH_PART_NUM IS NULL THEN B.WS_EXT_PH_PART_NUM ELSE A.WS_EXT_PH_PART_NUM END WS_EXT_PH_PART_NUM,
CASE WHEN A.WS_EXT_PH_NAME IS NULL THEN B.WS_EXT_PH_NAME ELSE A.WS_EXT_PH_NAME END WS_EXT_PH_NAME,
CASE WHEN A.WS_EXT_PH_BRTH_DATE IS NULL THEN B.WS_EXT_PH_BRTH_DATE ELSE A.WS_EXT_PH_BRTH_DATE END WS_EXT_PH_BRTH_DATE,
CASE WHEN A.WS_EXT_PH_ADDR_L1 IS NULL THEN B.WS_EXT_PH_ADDR_L1 ELSE A.WS_EXT_PH_ADDR_L1 END WS_EXT_PH_ADDR_L1,
CASE WHEN A.WS_EXT_PH_ADDR_L2 IS NULL THEN B.WS_EXT_PH_ADDR_L2 ELSE A.WS_EXT_PH_ADDR_L2 END WS_EXT_PH_ADDR_L2,
CASE WHEN A.WS_EXT_PH_ADDR_L3 IS NULL THEN B.WS_EXT_PH_ADDR_L3 ELSE A.WS_EXT_PH_ADDR_L3 END WS_EXT_PH_ADDR_L3,
CASE WHEN A.WS_EXT_PH_CITY IS NULL THEN B.WS_EXT_PH_CITY ELSE A.WS_EXT_PH_CITY END WS_EXT_PH_CITY,
CASE WHEN A.WS_EXT_PH_STATE IS NULL THEN B.WS_EXT_PH_STATE ELSE A.WS_EXT_PH_STATE END WS_EXT_PH_STATE,
CASE WHEN A.WS_EXT_PH_ZIP IS NULL THEN B.WS_EXT_PH_ZIP ELSE A.WS_EXT_PH_ZIP END WS_EXT_PH_ZIP,
CASE WHEN A.WS_EXT_PH_OMNI_VERSION IS NULL THEN B.WS_EXT_PH_OMNI_VERSION ELSE A.WS_EXT_PH_OMNI_VERSION END WS_EXT_PH_OMNI_VERSION,
CASE WHEN A.CHECK_SUM IS NULL THEN B.CHECK_SUM ELSE A.CHECK_SUM END CHECK_SUM,
CASE WHEN B.SOURCE_KEY IS NULL THEN 'NEW' WHEN  A.SOURCE_KEY IS NULL  THEN 'DELETE' WHEN  A.CHECK_SUM <> B.CHECK_SUM THEN 'UPDATE' END CHANGE_IND 
FROM CURR_CLN_DATE A FULL OUTER JOIN MYVOYAGE_MDM.RS_OMNI_VIPS_DAILY_PART_HEADER_PREV B ON A.SOURCE_KEY = B.SOURCE_KEY AND A.WS_EXT_PH_OMNI_VERSION = B.WS_EXT_PH_OMNI_VERSION
) WHERE CHANGE_IND IS NOT NULL;
